'''Kassoti''' was a [[Spice/Legends|spice]] variant mined on [[Rori/Legends|Rori]], a [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. The kassoti industry was represented by the [[Naboo Moon Mining Union]].

